A Perfect Foresight Liquidity Constrained Solution
Under perfect foresight in the presence of a liquidity constraint requiring b â‰¥ 0, this
appendix taxonomizes the varieties of the limiting consumption function cÌ€(m) that arise
under various parametric conditions. Results are summarized in table 1.

